criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Identify as African American or Black;

          -  Diagnosed by a healthcare provider with epilepsy or seizure disorder at least 3 months
             ago;

          -  Is mildly to moderately depressed or mildly to moderately anxious as determined by the
             PHQ-4;

          -  Willing to be audio-recorded during UPLIFT sessions

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Reports suicidal ideation within the past month
